Output examples/gifs/mods.gif

Set Height 900
Set Width 1600
Set Framerate 24

Hide
  Type `export PATH="$PWD/examples/demo-bin:$PATH"; clear`
  Enter
  Sleep 500ms
Show

Sleep 500ms

Type@25ms `printf '%s\n' '[{"name":"bubbletea"},{"name":"lipgloss"},{"name":"gum"},{"name":"vhs"}]'`

Sleep 500ms

Type@25ms ` | mods -f "rate this github org and summarize each repository"`

Enter

Sleep 6s
